H0.text: Which city was visited by Prince William in March 2011 after suffering two earthquakes in the preceeding six months. Christchurch

H1.text: Which city was visited by Prince William in March 2011 after suffering two earthquakes in the preceeding six months. Auckland

H2.text: Which city was visited by Prince William in March 2011 after suffering two earthquakes in the preceeding six months. Wellington

H3.text: Which city was visited by Prince William in March 2011 after suffering two earthquakes in the preceeding six months. ChCh

A4.text: On Saturday, 4 September 2010, a magnitude 7.1 earthquake struck Christchurch and the central Canterbury region at 4:35 am. On Tuesday, 22 February 2011, an earthquake measuring magnitude 6.3 struck the city at 12:51 pm.
